asset.name: FLEETS_Survey_CSS_FleetApp_UX-Survey

html.content:
%%=v(@submitted)=%%

Sharing your thoughts gets you better service.

You are our best chance of making Shell Fleet App live up to its promise, both for you and for new users. Please share your honest thoughts on the sign-up process and then hit Submit. All your answers will be anonymous. Just a few moments of your time will prove invaluable to us.

Question 1.

Please rate your experience of signing up to Shell Fleet App on a scale of 1 to 5, with 1 being very poor and 5 being excellent.

1   2   3   4   5

Question 1.1

We’re sorry to hear you didn’t have an easy time with the onboarding! What can we do to improve the registration process?

Question 2.

What made you choose for Shell Fleet App in the first place?

Competitive price Fuel credit to improve cashflow
Mobile app to manage my fleet
No deposit needed
Other

Multiple choice *

Question 3.

What other areas of improvement would you like to bring to our attention?

Thank you for your time.
